title: Heropanti-Album(2014)-320Kbps-JS MUSIC
description:
Director: Sabbir Khan
Cast: Tiger Shroff & Kriti Sanon
Music Director: Sajid-Wajid, Manj Musik & Mustafa Zahid

Heropanti is Jackie Shroff's son Tiger Shroff & Kriti Sanon's debut film produced by Sajid Nadiadwala and directed by Sabbir Khan. The soundtrack album is composed by Sajid-Wajid (3 songs), Manj Musik (2 songs) & Msutafa Zahid & Bilal Saeed (1 song).
